        <Parent_String>telecommunications buildings [300005399], communications buildings [300005371], communications structures [300122187], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
